Require the Inventory Committee to conduct a comprehensive physical count of all types of inventory items semiannually, prepare the RPCI, and submit the same to the Auditor concerned not later than July 31 and January 31 of each year for the first and second semesters, respectively. Also, invite a representative from the COA to act as a witness in the physical count; and
